<headline>Special Weather Statement issued October 04 at 6:42AM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Reduced Visibility this Morning due to Fog...
Fog has developed this morning in the valleys of Meagher County,
most notably in the Smith River Valley. Motorist should be
prepared for reduced visibility to generally 1 to 3 miles. Slow
down and use your low beam headlights when driving through fog.</description>
